OGRAPHY-DSC_2251%2520-low-res.jpeg\" class=\"team-profile-large_portfolio-header_image\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"team-header_background-icon-wrapper-copy\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.25\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/6924418b395e9ab3d12cfac8_shape-2.svg\" loading=\"eager\" class=\"team-header_background-icon-copy\"></div><div data-hidden=\"live\" class=\"dark_background\"></div></header><header class=\"section_team-profile-large_header-1\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid team-profile-large_header-1_content\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-left\"><h2>Committed to delivering the best outcome for you</h2></div><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-right\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>Rebecca Pickles is an Associate Conveyancer in our Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing team. Since joining in January 2019, she has developed broad experience across all aspects of residential conveyancing.</p><p>‍</p><p>Advising on freehold and leasehold sales and purchases, remortgages, transfers of equity, and new build transactions, Rebecca also specialises in Limited Company and Buy to Let matters. Her work frequently involves supporting landlords and investors on both single-property and portfolio transactions.</p><p>‍</p><p>She works closely with clients, lenders, brokers and estate agents to keep each transaction on track and ensure everything runs as smoothly as possible. Known for her approachable and supportive manner, Rebecca focuses on delivering a high-quality, client-centred service from start to finish.</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><section class=\"section_expertise-video w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"wrapper_wide-screen is-light\"><div class=\